Class FrameNumberVideoTimecode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.video.timecode.VideoTimecode

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class FrameNumberVideoTimecode
extends VideoTimecode
    This class allows video timecodes to be stored as frame numbers.
    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
